cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper discusses the performance of capsule networks in visual tasks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed improvement method involves regularization, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The method involves modifying the activation values of capsules, which is related to neural networks (cs.NE) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
